<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="365" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[809,1422,929,1359]" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">
This species was originally described from Guinean 
<collectingRegion box="[877,957,963,989]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">Nimba</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="BROSSET, A." box="[979,1151,963,989]" pageId="6" pageNumber="365" pagination="545 - 555" refId="ref12002" refString="BROSSET, A. 1985 [for 1984]. Chiropteres d'altitude du Mont Nimba (Guinee). Description d'une espece nouvelle, Hipposideros lamottei. Mammalia, 48: 545 - 555." type="journal article" year="1985">Brosset, 1985</bibRefCitation>
), and is probably endemic to that region (Monadjem 
<emphasis box="[1198,1250,996,1022]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">et al</emphasis>
., 2013 
<emphasis box="[1331,1346,996,1022]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">b</emphasis>
). Problems with identification (e.g. Koopman 
<emphasis box="[1345,1407,1030,1056]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">et al</emphasis>
., 1995) have been shown to result from an incorrect description of the 
<typeStatus box="[1027,1078,1097,1123]" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">type</typeStatus>
specimen (
<bibRefCitation author="DECHER, J. &amp; J. FAHR" pageId="6" pageNumber="365" pagination="5 - 30" refId="ref12281" refString="DECHER, J., and J. FAHR. 2007. A conservation assessment of bats (Chiroptera) of Draw River, Boi-Tano, and Krokosua Hills Forest Reserves in the Western Region of Ghana. Myotis, 43: 5 - 30." type="journal article" year="2007">Decher and Fahr, 2007</bibRefCitation>
; Monadjem 
<emphasis box="[1028,1084,1131,1157]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">et al</emphasis>
., 2013 
<emphasis box="[1170,1185,1131,1157]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">b</emphasis>
). This species was collected in 
<date box="[959,1140,1165,1191]" pageId="6" pageNumber="365" value="2008" valueMax="2012">
2008 and 
<quantity box="[1081,1140,1165,1191]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.11048" pageId="6" pageNumber="365" unit="in" value="2012.0">2012</quantity>
</date>
in mine adits at Pierré Richaud and Chateaux peaks, at 
<quantity box="[1217,1319,1198,1224]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="6" pageNumber="365" unit="m" value="1500.0">1,500 m</quantity>
a.s.l. in Guinean 
<collectingRegion box="[915,999,1232,1258]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">Nimba</collectingRegion>
. It is listed as Critically Endangered and its only known roosting sites are located within the mining concession in Guinean 
<collectingRegion box="[1229,1309,1299,1325]" country="Liberia" name="Nimba" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">Nimba</collectingRegion>
(Mickleburgh 
<emphasis box="[885,937,1333,1359]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="365">et al</emphasis>
., 2008).
</paragraph>
